resources.string:
First of all we have to create a Android resource directory named "anim" and create Animation resource file from there then use : For Scale :
android:fromXScale="1" android:toXScale="4" android:fromYScale="1" android:toYScale="4" android:pivotY="50%" android:pivotX="50%" android:duration = "4000"
just like that then in onclicklistener method: Animation scale = AnimationUtils.loadAnimation(getApplicationContext(),R.anim.scale); textView.startAnimation(scale);
